fined as:              max(red, green, blue)Lightness is defined as:              ( max(red, green, blue) + min(red, green, blue) ) /2Luminance is defined as:              0.3 * red + 0.59 * green + 0.11 * blue©Bergen senter for elektronisk kunst, 2001